cused&lt;br&gt;ethics&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+7+8]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;   66k lives-eq/$1k · 70% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Wild insects (humane pesticides) · 30%&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Pearce)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1z27gR%2Fis7nl4rpTJFUu9y3Rknlu8y5%2BQyttObmyijQCQkoSYJFgBN63K%2B394FQEqUpdRM9cVDi9hnn33FLr%2BehHRBski94SE9GZ%2B023B%2Bfg53grAEFIdAkN%2FX%2BJAnMM181%2BtCzkUUPjCaQ%2B7N%2FFlvNpgNoSEVT2HY1MLTBEEupMziVDGeQLBCrDG4kBLBgxUjkYbyRj54sCBiRnKynq2ymCSyfOEDSVhMIjmTPKb5iqjyTQ8WmcoELQRmMVGKilnO1GoWMhnwLFEsWZbHBxug4iCZRXwDNgSZLRZUoMBswYNM0tCQn5BgBWRrAZNA4MNarfB5wSIK6Jvta9kGpRmSMJQtEBQdyhIqgQsDJugpGk5iiuqZxN%2FVilqf%2FE2iMUlgMM4g4HHKpea%2BOYCySUgREX9i0qBJRZKQRDyhEGPEIge%2BbAIyefiiqWpx%2BpjSQKHgA4kyCnxhELaxcwzYayoVzLM1ZFqNFpS0atgYbleCxSn8SiOMFIUPgv8bca30j5P3k5uLu8klzNewpAkVRFEnXZeJQkOmdtz0Cl%2B2IEH%2FGzLak4hksD4mARVKmxxzgQmy8Zi0Z607SJpGjEoHbtexE%2FFlwgXGtvE17bUgHfWemgbLRGvk%2FgBv3p6Zk3OqiP01FXxO5ixiConMuTY71Fn%2ByW2B99mBKxIojjrRVguFB1Idg0S1QHKgOjG4WGLkJp%2Fyy4vr39p%2F%2BQxzGvEcU1nLmgjTR3yO1iiO2OhVg4W6wyxQNhYYPYrpi%2BYvIp6h1AoDf1nkL5zvG4j147hDY6Z%2BHD41AUxyISbakFO2XCE2VpugxFTACr2l81BC447HRLL7M%2FgXGqTf%2Ba7vorM22f9BMKSu1oc1e45XKO47vUIxfVSCVNSSB4yfhkabaYJptMH%2Btnpbyf%2Fb6g493Zitn%2FuF%2FhQlTxWLKfwdAqKIVIKn6FZd5UlGTNnqaiXi1KopKqFxQ2JJ1%2B1bzK0E%2FnR%2FaK8FPEh4z0W4IpmEPz2np388w%2B50jskKZVdpFql6yQSWAFA