ke the meat-eater problem it is a near-term get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism, where the cropland bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 9 meat_eater_problem → 10 net_negative_animal_lives → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWG1v2zgS%2FiuD4PbO7jqKJL8nlwPSxtktNu0WSXrFoilUWqJtXiRRR1JRvN3sb78hKdlyom4E%2BD7EUCTymWdeOcNvBxFdkDxWb3hED44Pjo7g9PQUbgRhKSgOoSC%2Fr%2FGhSOE2911vAAUXcXTPaAGFF%2FjBMBgHk2AaeG7gTaAjFc%2FAm3Q1ym2KaGdS5kmmGE8hXCHoMbiQEcHDFSOxxvSmPniwICIgBVkHqzwhqaw%2B%2BEBSlpBYBpIntFgRVX0ZwiJXuaDlhiAhSlERFEytgojJkOepYumyWj7eAJULSRDzDdgEZL5YUIEbggUPc0mj6tMUEkpUgH%2B4KRN8HtNkQ9uFlKogpUui2D0NrIggxueNBmgUyVlcfpPGJjMSroBsDcMkEPiwVit8XrCYAtp%2B%2B1kegdKKkyiSPRAUHcZSFMCFARP0EO1JEooEmcT3akWtqf8h0UZpaDBOIORJxqU2yWYB7k0jioj4illqUpE0IjFPKSQYEbEDXzcOn91%2F1VT1dvqQ0VDhxnsS5xT4wiBsY8MxYK%2BpVDDP15BrMXqjpHXFjuF6JViSwScaYwBQ%2BCD4fxDX7v5p9n52dXYzO4f5GpY0pQJ94GTrKhBpxNSOmV7hxx6k6FZDRlsSkQzWxzSkQmmVEy4w7jYWk3atNQfJsphR6cD1OnFivky5QJ91vmXDHmTT4WPXYBlvTd0f4M3bE7NyThWxb3V8kDmLmUIic67VjnQWfXZ74H1x4IKEiqNM1NVC4YJM%2ByBVPQwToDowuFii52afi%2FOzy9%2BO%2FvYF5jTmBWaI3ms8TB%2FwOV7jdsRGqxoslB3lobK%2BoDpqU4nqL2Ke464VOv68TAs4fa4gpqXjToya%2BnHy2AUwwYWYqENB2XKF2JjEAlNBR9EKraXjUELnhidEsrsT%2BDcqpL%2F5ru%2BisTZJ9UEwpK7WzZI9xysFj5xhKZg%2BKEFqYsk9%2Bk9Do840xTDaYH9fvC0Qf611nx5u1NbPo1J%2BhjsPFUso%2FAghUUQqwTM0qy4eaU5M2upsJeLQiikzoXNFEknXR9cYWyn86f5wtBZwL%2BE9F9GK5BL%2B9JyhfnmCRe8UgxWqYtUtQ%2FWcCUwBoKheaFSvBUWG2ULEGiMixSIQMnzuwevZxa9XMxvYBsFaDQ3Rw%2FTAqEywdKbqEAtfuEJfbiwA1x%2FfvTu7%2Bs2GDFYYKwST%2BI5GBmnOFQ2ho2MJzt6fo46CEUwlG4FdB27QJIs8jsvoPJyvD%2B0TYMKze2snm6%2BWGpZnq5BdZnTi9zQ1qFh6MAtygY9ljttSqo8iFBSztCIm%2F5uz5TKmR4ahPPoni%2F7lVC9t5TIJhRUCE1NXClQcYX59P4MsJlZWWT5JpAsMxQBbbwsYFlqCMnXRQt1ZirINAiacXWmrI8Y4z7NfmLZsek7i9QcqPsqoOdZGzsifTvuT4XTi%2Bf2x62G8DTcp57reeDoZ9weeOx4PPX%2FsDcpYfOI%2FLHgmCMpE1wSCO8tgx