er human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 9 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWH9v2zgS%2FSqD4PbO7tmKJP92LwekjbNbXNotkhSLRV24tETb3EqijqSieLvZz75DUrLlWIsI8B9tVYt882bmDTmj72chXZEsUm95SM%2BmZ%2BfncHFxAfeCsAQUh0CQ37f4kCcwz3zX60PORRQ%2BMJpD7i38xWAxWkygJRVPYdLWm%2BcJglxKmcWpYjyBYINYU3AhJYIHG0YiDeVNfPBgRcSC5GS72GQxSWT5wgeSsJhEciF5TPMNUeWbAawylQlabFjERCkqFjlTm0XIZMCzRLFkXS4f7YCKhWQR8R3YBGJK1AL%2F4JtU8GVEY8N%2BRoINkL0LTAKBj1u1wecViyhgcPav5TkoTZGEoeyAoBhRllAJXBgwQbvoOYkpWmESf1cbaoPyL4neJIHBeA0Bj1MuNfndAtybhBQR8ScmDZpUJAlJxBMKMaYscuDrLiOzh6%2Baqt5OH1MaKNz4QKKMAl8ZhH3yHAP2hkoFy2wLmTajN0padWwKdxvB4hR%2BoRGmisJHwX9DXLv7x9mH2e3l%2FewKlltY04QKDKSTbkul0JCpgzC9wpcdSDABhoyOJCIZrE9JQIXSLsdcoEJ2EZN2rQ0HSdOIUenA3TZ2Ir5OuMDktr6ngw6kk8FT22CZbE3cH%2BDtu9dm5ZIqYn%2FVSSZLFjGFRJZcux1qmX92O%2BB9ceCaBIqjTfTVQuGCVOcgUR2QHKgWBhdrzNzsc351efPr%2BT%2B%2BwJJGPEct670mw%2FQRn6MtbkdsjKrBQtthFiibC6qll0h03%2Br5qtAuXBz7NoUe7bpj46J9Hj61ATQk7uwqFlP4NwREEakETxFbaz3JiNGuliwRXWumkEPrlsSSbs%2FvMMAJ%2FOn%2BcL4V8CDhAxfhhmQS%2FvScgf7xNdboBWYMytpqF%2Fm6YgJ1AHS10v%2BgjUpkUpQMEVsMS4KVEDB87sCb2fXPtzObXYOQU7be6FrtoEYwNTFWeqK6WKfBBpOyiwDcfXr%2F%2FvL2Vxs3LDNrBJX8jYYGackVDaClAwqXH67QR8EI6smmoe3APYZklUVRkaLuctu1T4CqZw82Tla0lhqeJtYhu8z4xB9oYlCx%2FlAKmcDHQugRe8Ck6wMTDUUsKYnJ%2F2dsvY7ouWEoz%2F%2FDwv865Y%2B2fI2qsExQnbpc0HGE%2BfnDDNKIWFvFGUJCXWX0gWJgd1WMpw1Bm7py0XeWoG2DgKqzK%2B0RMU%2BQb%2Fo%2FpiObXJFo%2B5GKTzKs19rQGfqTSW88mIw9vz